This is a shell file that sets up after-install EndeavourOS to my personal specification

Below is a list of all current features: 
-Installs Required and Preferential Packages
-Installs Hyprland Desktop Environment
-Sets up Default LightDM (With Greeter)
-Installs and Configures KVM with VirtManager
-Customize Greeter

Below is a list of all future features:
-Custom KVM VM Setups
-Setup GPU Passthrough Prerequisites
-Other Customizations 